attachments.title: Scorpion Brings the Stupidest, Most Batshit Insane Hacker Scene Ever
attachments.text: So Scorpion debuted last night on CBS, bringing us the thrilling tale of "geniuses" who help DHS by setting up wifi access points in restaurants. Yes, that is a true plot point. It all leads to this scene, whose true meaning I will unfold for you so that you can appreciate the full amazing awfulness.
